          <title>Overpaid by Social Security? You&#8217;ll now owe 100% of the repayment</title>
          <description><![CDATA[NEW YORK (PIX11) – If you accidentally got overpaid through your Social Security benefits, you’ll have to pay 100% of it back starting in late March, the agency announced on Monday. The overpayment withholding rate was previously 10%.]]></description>
